aZtPVS1Kzv77bFeUw1al5lUmLlwm52UoN0Icw&oe=671A3C04"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "677824147318518", "uri": "https://scontent-xsp1-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/54823267_677824150651851_3688777864047447478_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jqOFvNpT8WIQ7kNvgHeLwra&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-xsp1-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCsUc_nQXJXQYYE-wRL6d2xgvfkrkUn5yL4TBOHVxR0rA&oe=671A42EE"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "329704216222612", "uri": "https://scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75250460_329704219555945_6993099148500521476_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=io9CH9JanVwQ7kNvgF2vdvz&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAtZwKpgJsXnvEnLrZ6m4uA1dCP_6fw3mT8K4uMUVPFWg&oe=671A4CD3"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "627211022861814", "uri": "https://scontent-xsp1-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031653_627211026195147_859210511188470322_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=iCYWO7RRk_IQ7kNvgH3ZMjy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-xsp1-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBNsyEK0CKwGQG0el2oC99ma9U9HDcEiFRaItzWeI-Ziw&oe=671A4728"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "VRLegs", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Welcome to \"VRLegs\", where the thrill of parkour meets the immersive world of virtual reality. Step into a realm where your movements are fluid, intuitive, and empowering. Our state-of-the-art locomotion system redefines how you move, jump, and traverse in the VR space, offering an unparalleled sensation of freedom.\n\nChallenge friends or team up in heart-pounding multiplayer tag matches. Navigate complex terrains, leap across buildings, and experience the exhilaration of real-time chases. As you master your environment, you'll discover new strategies, shortcuts, and moves to stay one step ahead or elude capture.\n\nWhether you're a parkour enthusiast or new to the world of VR, \"VRLegs\" promises an adrenaline-pumping experience like no other. Join the revolution, find 